title: Episode 567 | "Boo Bop Tour"
description:
On this week’s episode, Parks discusses Tua Tagovailoa’s concussion injury (14:25). Joe and Ish debate if Ime Udoka was wrong for being with the owner’s wife (24:05). Ice explains why DaBaby’s projections are so low (53:30). Joe found some new conspiracies (1:08:55). Updates on the PNB Rock tragedy (1:20:50). The guys discuss new music (2:08:45) + More!

Sleeper Picks

Joe | Chxrry22 - “The Falls”

Ice | Albee Al - “CASH RULES” (Ft. Mozzy)

Parks | Prodigy - “Walk Out” (Ft. DJ Premier)

Ish | V. Cartier - “Come Down”
